<p>John and Dave are back with a great show today filled with some fantastic answers. First a tip that (here&rsquo;s the free giveaway) indicates that WPA does protect you from Firesheep&rsquo;s antics, then it&rsquo;s on to fixing pesky iTunes firewall dialogs, killing processes, preference fixing and more. Subscribe today, support your two favorite geeks, and enjoy!</p>
